summary: Yo some of the posts I’ve seen comparing representation in Good Omens to that in Supernatural is coming dangerously close to...
body:
Yo some of the posts I’ve seen comparing representation in Good Omens to that in Supernatural is coming dangerously close to just straight up shitting on people who LIKE Supernatural and Destiel and if we would like- not- do that. It’d be great. I was never much for Supernatural and Destiel but fandom should first and foremost be FUN and I feel like this is forgotten in the race to find the most ideologically pure piece of media 

Let the Supernatural fans have fun. Let the Supernatural fans have fun in the Good Omens fanbase. Don’t be a buzzkill, don’t be That Asshole. 

(And please don’t stop making your GO/SN crossover gifs they bring me UNREASONABLE amounts of joy)
